      'office glass partition cost',
      'glass wall installation for renovation'
    ]
  },
  {
    type: 'Shop & Retail Owners',
    problem: 'Storefront glass, display windows',
    keywords: [
      'shop front glass installer',
      'retail glass display contractor',
      'storefront glass replacement',
      'glass shoplot door installation'
